(define/contract (max-number-of-alloys n k budget composition stock cost)
  (-> exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer? (listof (listof exact-integer?)) (listof exact-integer?) (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let ((max-alloys 0))
    (for ([i (in-range k)])
      (let* ((machine-comp (list-ref composition i))
             (cost-per-alloy (for/fold ([total-cost 0]) ([comp (in-list machine-comp)] [stock-qty (in-list stock)] [cost-qty (in-list cost)])
                               (+ total-cost (* (max 0 (- comp stock-qty)) cost-qty))))
             (alloys-possible (if (> cost-per-alloy 0) (floor (/ budget cost-per-alloy)) 0)))
        (set! max-alloys (max max-alloys alloys-possible))))
    max-alloys))
